choices.text:
buying a Mercedes for my sister. Most of the times in the university, I spent my time writing and reading rather than going out to parties s I cant afford riding taxi to go out for parties and drinking with girls. That kind of life is for the rich not poor. I thought going to US would change my poor life into rich one. However I did not realize going to US is still a dream because I need to pay tuition to the college in my home country before I received the documents to apply for US visa.

Another commenter writes:

I’ll say:  I didn’t apply.  This was fortunate because if I had, I couldn’t have gotten even an American high school diploma: I did not graduate.  It says on the shreaded paper taped to my file that I never turned in my final high school transcript despite 3 letters and a phone call before the agreed deadline.  School, Street and other… not a fan.  That’s my own fault, but that aside…Я было бы на удивение, хлопоты не позволяют мне учиться в школе. Конечно, создал бы это жалобы и жалких ситуациях, и, если я даже имею возможность, высокое образование иметься ввиду на каждом уг
